\c 29
\s Isivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* loIsrayeli elizweni lakoMowabi
\p
\v 1 La ngamazwi esivumelwano iN\nd kosi\nd* eyamlaya uMozisi ukusenza labantwana bakoIsrayeli elizweni lakoMowabi, ngaphandle kwesivumelwano eyayisenze labo eHorebe\x + 5.2,3.\x*.
\p
\v 2 UMozisi wasebiza uIsrayeli wonke, wathi kubo: Lina libonile konke iN\nd kosi\nd* eyakwenza phambi kwamehlo enu elizweni leGibhithe, kuFaro lakuzo zonke inceku zakhe lakulo lonke ilizwe lakhe\x + Eks. 19.4.\x*,
\v 3 izilingo ezinkulu amehlo akho azibonileyo, izibonakaliso lalezozimangaliso ezinkulu\x + 4.34.\x*.
\v 4 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* kayilinikanga inhliziyo yokuqedisisa lamehlo okubona lendlebe zokuzwa kuze kube lamuhla\x + Isa. 6.9,10. 63.17. Joha. 8.43. Seb. 28.26,27.\x*.
\v 5 Ngilihambise iminyaka engamatshumi amane enkangala\x + 1.3.\x*. Izembatho zenu kaziguganga phezu kwenu, lenyathela lakho kaliguganga enyaweni lwakho\x + 8.4.\x*;
\v 6 kalidlanga sinkwa, kalinathanga iwayini lokunathwayo okulamandla, ukuze lazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + 8.3. Eks. 16.4.\x*.
\v 7 Ekufikeni kwenu kulindawo, uSihoni inkosi yeHeshiboni loOgi inkosi yeBashani baphuma ukumelana lathi empini, kodwa sabatshaya\x + Nani 21.21-24,33-35. Dute. 2.32. 3.1.\x*,
\v 8 sathatha ilizwe labo, salinika laba yilifa kwabakoRubeni lakwabakoGadi lakungxenye yesizwe sakoManase\x + Nani 32.33. Dute. 3.12,13.\x*.
\v 9 Ngakho gcinani amazwi alesisivumelwano liwenze\x + 4.6.\x*, ukuze liphumelele kukho konke elikwenzayo\x + Josh. 1.7. 1 Sam. 18.5,14,15,30. 1 Kho. 2.3. Jer. 10.21.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Lina lonke limi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu lamuhla, inhloko zenu, izizwe zenu, abadala benu, lezinduna zenu, wonke amadoda akoIsrayeli\x + 16.18. Josh. 1.10.\x*,
\v 11 abantwanyana benu, omkenu, lowemzini ophakathi kwenkamba yakho, kusukela kumgamuli wenkuni zakho kuze kube kumukhi wamanzi akho\x + Josh. 9.21,23,27.\x*,
\v 12 ukwedlulela esivumelwaneni seN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho lesifungweni sayo, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho esenza lawe lamuhla\x + Neh. 10.29.\x*,
\v 13 ukuze ikumise lamuhla ube yisizwe sayo, lokuthi yona ibe nguNkulunkulu wakho\x + 28.9.\x*, njengokutsho kwayo kuwe\x + Eks. 6.7.\x* lanjengokufunga kwayo kuboyihlo, kuAbrahama, kuIsaka lakuJakobe\x + Gen. 17.7. Gen. 50.24.\x*.
\v 14 Njalo kangisenzi lani lodwa lesisivumelwano\x + Jer. 31.31,32,33. Heb. 8.8-10.\x* lalesisifungo\x + Neh. 10.29.\x*,
\v 15 kodwa lalowo olapha lathi, omiyo lamuhla phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu, njalo lalowo ongekho lapha lathi lamuhla\x + Seb. 2.39.\x*.
\v 16 Ngoba lina liyazi ukuthi sahlala njani elizweni leGibhithe, lokuthi sadabula njani phakathi kwezizwe eladabula kuzo;
\v 17 njalo libonile izinengiso zazo, lezithombe zazo, isigodo lelitshe, isiliva legolide, ezazilazo.
\v 18 Hlezi kube khona phakathi kwenu indoda kumbe owesifazana kumbe usapho kumbe isizwe, onhliziyo yakhe iphambuka lamuhla isuka eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wethu ukuyakhonza onkulunkulu balezizizwe. Hlezi kube khona phakathi kwenu impande ethela izithelo ezilobuhlungu\x + Seb. 8.23. Heb. 12.15.\x* lezibabayo\x + Isam. 8.11.\x*.
\v 19 Njalo kuzakuthi nxa esizwa amazwi alesisiqalekiso, azibusise enhliziyweni yakhe esithi: Ngizakuba lokuthula lanxa ngihamba ebuqholweni benhliziyo yami; ukuze kuqedwe okumanzi\x + Isa. 30.1.\x* kanye lokomileyo.
\v 20 IN\nd kosi\nd* kayiyikuvuma ukumthethelela, kodwa khona intukuthelo yeN\nd kosi\x + Hlab. 74.1.\x*\nd* lobukhwele bayo kuzathunqela leyondoda, njalo sonke isiqalekiso esibhaliweyo egwalweni lolu sizalala phezu kwayo\x + Hlab. 79.5.\x*, leN\nd kosi\nd* icitshe ibizo layo lisuke ngaphansi kwamazulu.\x + 9.14.\x*
\v 21 LeN\nd kosi\nd* izayehlukanisela ububi iyikhuphe kuzo zonke izizwe zakoIsrayeli, njengazo zonke iziqalekiso zesivumelwano ezibhaliweyo egwalweni lwalumlayo.
\v 22 Khona sizakuthi isizukulwana esizayo, abantwana benu, abazavela emva kwenu, lowezizwe ovela elizweni elikhatshana, lapho bebona inhlupheko zalelilizwe lezifo iN\nd kosi\nd* eligulise ngazo\x + 29.24.\x*,
\v 23 ilizwe lonke lalo lizakuba yisibabule letshwayi lokutshiswa, alihlanyelwanga, kalimilisi, kakulalatshani obumila kulo\x + Hlab. 107.34. Hlu. 9.45. Jer. 17.6. Hez. 47.11. Zef. 2.9.\x*, njengokubhujiswa kweSodoma leGomora, iAdima leZeboyimi, iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayibhubhisa entukuthelweni yayo lelakeni lwayo\x + Gen. 19.24,25,29. Jer. 20.16.\x*,
\v 24 lazo zonke izizwe zizakuthi\x + 29.22.\x*: Kungani iN\nd kosi\nd* yenze kanje kulelilizwe\x + 1 Kho. 9.8,9. Jer. 22.8,9.\x*? Kuyini ukuvutha kwalolulaka olukhulu\x + Eks. 11.8.\x*?
\v 25 Khona bazakuthi: Ngoba batshiyile isivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu waboyise, eyasenza labo ekubakhupheni kwayo elizweni leGibhithe.
\v 26 Bahamba bakhonza abanye onkulunkulu babakhothamela, onkulunkulu abangabaziyo, eyayingababelanga.
\v 27 Lentukuthelo yeN\nd kosi\nd* yalivuthela lelilizwe, ukwehlisela kulo zonke iziqalekiso ezibhaliweyo egwalweni lolu.
\v 28 Njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yabasiphuna elizweni labo ngentukuthelo langolaka langenzondo enkulu, yabaphosela kwelinye ilizwe njengalamuhla\x + 1 Kho. 14.15. 2 Lan. 7.20.\x*.
\v 29 Imfihlo ngezeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu, kodwa izinto ezembuliweyo zingezethu lezabantwana bethu kuze kube nininini, ukwenza wonke amazwi alumlayo.
